{"type":"message","id":"cedcdadf","parentId":"b078c938","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:02.207Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 16:02 CDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Message for William: Tony says he loves the team. Start now on outreach drafting: write 3 tight outreach templates (job lead, company intro, follow-up)."}],"timestamp":1773090122204}}
{"type":"message","id":"19ca3b5e","parentId":"cedcdadf","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:07.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are three tight outreach templates as requested:\n\n1. Job Lead Outreach Template:\n---\nSubject: Exciting Opportunity - [Job Title] at [Company Name]\n\nHi [Recipient's Name],\n\nTony here. I wanted to share an exciting opportunity at [Company Name] for the [Job Title] role. We think you’d be a great fit and would love to discuss how your skills align with what we’re looking for.\n\nLet me know if you’re open to a quick chat!\n\nBest,  \nTony\n\n2. Company Introduction Outreach Template:\n---\nSubject: Introducing [Company Name] - Innovation in [Industry]\n\nHi [Recipient's Name],\n\nTony here from [Company Name]. We’re passionate about [brief value proposition or unique aspect]. I’d love to connect and share how we might help you [achieve specific goal/solve a problem].\n\nAre you available for a brief conversation this week?\n\nThanks,  \nTony\n\n3. Follow-Up Outreach Template:\n---\nSubject: Following Up on My Previous Message\n\nHi [Recipient's Name],\n\nJust following up on my last note about [topic/job opportunity/company]. I’m eager to connect and explore how we can work together.\n\nPlease let me know if you have any questions or want to schedule a chat.\n\nBest regards,  \nTony\n\nWill that work for you?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ea24518bd8a8eed0069af354c061081948663b0ee00303b18\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":8498,"output":265,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8763,"cost":{"input":0.0033992000000000002,"output":0.00042400000000000006,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0038232}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090122207}}
